Problem Statement:
------------------
Your task is to display a Birthday Count Down for the user.

1- Add an input for Date on the page and label it Date of birth.
2- Add a button on this page, label it "When is my next bithday". 
3- When button is clicked, Calculate how many days till users next birthday
   based on the input
4- Print the number of days as "X days till your next birthday"

(e.g. : If the user input their Date of Birth as 3/18/1990 - 
message should be "365 days till your next birthday")
